name: War
description: Indian agent Khalid goes on a mission to hunt and eliminate his former mentor, the country's top agent Kabir who has gone rogue. A deadly war begins.

name: Saaho
description: In a fictional megalopolis, a stunning underworld theft triggers a fierce power struggle among the gangsters, with an enigmatic cop on their trail.

name: Kabir Singh
description: An exalted but short-fused surgeon plunges into a spiral of drugs, alcohol and rage after his intense relationship with his girlfriend turbulently ends.

name: Uri: The Surgical Strike
description: Indian army special forces execute a covert operation, avenging the killing of fellow army men at their base by a terrorist group.

name: Bharat
description: At the cusp of India's birth as an Independent nation, a family makes an arduous journey to freedom at a cost. A young boy Bharat, makes a promise to his Father that he will keep his family together no matter what.

name: Good Newwz
description: Two couples with the same surname pursue in-vitro fertilization and wait for their upcoming babies. Trouble ensues when they find that the sperms of each couple have been mixed with each other.

name: Bigil
description: Michael gives up his dream of becoming a footballer after his father's murder. However, a friend convinces him to coach a women's football team and turn his life around.

name: Housefull 4
description: Three couples who get separated from each other due to an evil ploy, reincarnate after 600 years and meet each other as history repeats itself again and their respective partners get mixed up this time.

name: Mission Mangal
description: Based on true events of the Indian Space Research Organisation (ISRO) successfully launching the Mars Orbiter Mission (Mangalyaan), making it the least expensive mission to Mars.

name: Sye Raa Narasimha Reddy
description: A historical action epic inspired by the life of Uyyalawada Narasimha Reddy, who revolted against the atrocities of East India Company 10 years before the Sepoy Mutiny.

name: Gully Boy
description: A coming-of-age story based on the lives of street rappers in Mumbai.

name: Total Dhamaal
description: A group of people learn about a hidden treasure and then they race to find it and claim it.

name: Dabangg 3
description: Chulbul Pandey encounters an enemy from his past, and his origin story as the fearless cop unfolds.

name: Petta
description: A hostel warden becomes the target of a dreaded politician and his gangster son, but little do they realize that it is they who should fear him.

name: Super 30
description: Based on the life of Patna-based mathematician Anand Kumar who runs the famed Super 30 program for IIT aspirants in Patna.

name: Chhichhore
description: A tragic incident forces Anirudh, a middle-aged man, to take a trip down memory lane and reminisce his college days along with his friends, who were labelled as losers.

name: Kesari
description: Based on an incredible true story of the Battle of Saragarhi in which an army of 21 Sikhs fought against 10,000 Afghans in 1897.

name: Dream Girl
description: Rom-com Movie, directed by Raaj Shaandilyaa, stars Ayushmann Khurrana who plays a 'dream girl'. In every love story, there is always one trying to win the heart of the other, who could be the 'dream girl'.

name: Viswasam
description: A village ruffian, who settles disputes in his native, takes on a big shot when he tries to sort out the rough patch in his marriage after several years.

name: Maharshi
description: A story about Rishi and his quest for success in different stages of life from being a US-based businessman to being a champion for the poor downtrodden farmers.

name: Bala
description: It tells the story of a man who is balding prematurely and how he copes up with the situation.

name: Kalank
description: The lives of six enigmatic characters become entangled whilst in search of love, but separated by the dichotomy between the two worlds of Husnabad, a town in North India.

name: Badla
description: A dynamic young entrepreneur finds herself locked in a hotel room with the corpse of her dead lover. She hires a prestigious lawyer to defend her and they work together to figure out what actually happened.

name: F2: Fun and Frustration
description: After Venky, Varun also gets married thinking he can keep the wife in control but both of them get frustrated with the marital life which generates fun.

name: Manikarnika: The Queen of Jhansi
description: Story of Rani Lakshmibai, one of the leading figures of the Indian Rebellion of 1857, and her resistance to the British Rule.

name: De De Pyaar De
description: A 50-year-old single father faces disapproval from his family and his ex-wife when he falls in love with a 26-year-old woman.

name: Kanchana 3
description: A young man who gets easily scared is possessed by a ghost that is seeking revenge.

name: Lucifer
description: A political Godfather dies and a lot of thieves dressed up as politicians took over the rule. Question arises regarding the successor of the God, unfolding few names, along with the God's most beloved angel, Lucifer.

name: Luka Chuppi
description: Pretending to be married in order to cohabitate, a small-town couple lands in endless awkward situations to hide the truth from their orthodox families.

name: Batla House
description: In 2008, a violent shootout with terror suspects leaves one police officer struggling to hunt down the fugitives and justify the police action.

name: Pati Patni Aur Woh
description: Chintu Tyagi is an ordinary, middle class man who finds himself torn between his wife and another woman.

name: Kaithi
description: Dilli, an ex-convict, endeavours to meet his daughter for the first time after leaving prison. However, his attempts are interrupted due to a drug raid planned by Inspector Bejoy.

name: Nerkonda Paarvai
description: When three young women are implicated in a crime, a retired lawyer steps forward to help them clear their names.

name: Vinaya Vidheya Rama
description: When the happiness of his family is held to ransom by a violent crime lord, Ram sets out on a quest to destroy his nemesis and his criminal empire.

name: Student of the Year 2
description: A student must face off against bullies and overcome hurdles, both academic and romantic, to win his college's coveted Student of the Year trophy.

name: Article 15
description: In the rural heartlands of India, an upright police officer sets out on a crusade against violent caste-based crimes and discrimination.

name: Namma Veettu Pillai
description: A brother who dotes on his sister is forced into a situation where he has to get her married to a ruffian with whom he is at loggerheads. Can their relationship survive?

name: Kaappaan
description: A Special Protection Group officer has to identify the threat to the prime minister, who he is protecting, and also the nation.

name: iSmart Shankar
description: A contract killer escapes after murdering a politician and must help the cops find a murderer after a slain officer's memories are transferred to his brain.

name: Asuran
description: The teenage son of a farmer from an underprivileged caste kills a rich, upper caste landlord. How the pacifist farmer saves his hot-blooded son is the rest of the story.

name: Majili
description: After being abandoned by his lover, Anshu, Poorna takes to alcohol and is forced to marry his neighbour, Sravani. However, he soon discovers her unrequited love for him and falls for her.

name: Mardaani 2
description: A 21-year old boy Sunny has a penchant for sexually assaulting and killing girls. He's locked horns with top cop Shivani Shivaji Roy. Will she nab him?

name: Venky Mama
description: A story of nephew and a son which revolves around their emotions and village drama and army based story.

name: Marjaavaan
description: Raghu and Zoya are enjoying their lives together until a gang leader with harmful intentions turns their world upside down.

name: Prati Roju Pandaage
description: With only a few weeks left to live, an aging grandfather is visited by his grandson who wishes to fulfill his desires.

name: NGK
description: An educated do-gooder is forced to enter politics in order to serve the society. But, will the old guard make way and allow him to do that?

name: Comali
description: A youngster in his mid-30s goes through a series of struggles after coming to terms with the fact that he was in coma for 16 years.

name: Kurukshetra
description: The film is based on the epic Mahabharata and poet Ranna's Gadhayuddha's story narrates the events of the Kurukshetra war.

name: Shadaa
description: Amidst pressures from his parents to hurry up and wed, a young man seeks his perfect match. After many failed attempts with matchmakers, his parents are delighted when their son finally meets the woman of his dreams but things do ...

name: Jersey
description: A failed cricketer decides to revive his cricketing career in his late 30's despite everyone being skeptical of his ability to do so.
